<li>Conviction Calculation:<br>
<span class="katex--display"><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><mtext>Conviction</mtext><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>A</mi><mo>→</mo><mi>C</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mtext>Support</mtext><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>C</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mtext>Confidence</mtext><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>A</mi><mo>→</mo><mi>C</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>0.80</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>0.75</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>0.20</mn><mn>0.25</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn mathvariant="bold">0.80</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\text{Conviction}(A \rightarrow C) = \frac{1 - \text{Support}(C)}{1 - \text{Confidence}(A \rightarrow C)} = \frac{1 - 0.80}{1 - 0.75} = \frac{0.20}{0.25} = \mathbf{0.80}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 1em; vertical-align: -0.25em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">Conviction</span></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal">A</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.277778em;"></span><span class="mrel">→</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.277778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 1em; vertical-align: -0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right: 0.07153em;">C</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.277778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.277778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 2.363em; vertical-align: -0.936em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mopen nulldelimiter"></span><span class="mfrac"